cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IT, cs.DS, cs.CV 

The paper introduces a new distribution and explores its theoretical properties, making it likely to fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The distribution is also used in semi-supervised auto-encoding tasks, which could place it under information theory (cs.IT), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), or computer vision (cs.CV).
